The paper discusses a new ensemble, deep learning approach for classification, which is a popular topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper specifically focuses on image and text classification as well as face recognition, which suggests that it could fall under the categories of computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of deep neural networks (DNN), convolutional neural networks (CNN), and recurrent neural networks (RNN), which are all subfields of machine learning and could place the paper under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) or neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
